\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Describing the rigorous preparation process, Carla explained the strict rules governing the competition, from the precise weight of finger foods to the compelling storytelling behind each dish.\", \"from\": 4140, \"to\": 4333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4185, \"end\": 4190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carla_Connor\", \"score\": 0.9999907184495535, \"rank\": 9.281523166521274e-06, \"text\": \"Carla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carla_Connor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carla_Connor\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rigorous preparation process\", \"from\": 4151, \"to\": 4183}, {\"ngram\": \"the strict rules\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4217}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4243}, {\"ngram\": \"the precise weight\", \"from\": 4250, \"to\": 4268}, {\"ngram\": \"finger foods\", \"from\": 4272, \"to\": 4284}, {\"ngram\": \"each dish\", \"from\": 4323, \"to\": 4332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"You get marked on methodical work, taste, look, and even the story behind the food.\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"methodical work\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4378}, {\"ngram\": \"the food\", \"from\": 4419, \"to\": 4427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a challenge, but it's huge and massive.\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is even rules down to each element including the weight of the finger food, which needs to weigh between 10 and 15 grams, otherwise you lose marks.\\\"\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4630, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"even rules\", \"from\": 4485, \"to\": 4495}, {\"ngram\": \"each element\", \"from\": 4504, \"to\": 4516}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 4527, \"to\": 4537}, {\"ngram\": \"the finger